{"tid":1243392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實而家唔係最好時機分化林鄭政府團隊?","createTime":"2019-06-19T12:25:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T13:10:34.000Z","uid":264426,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"354bf75dcec62e79de3d4833fa59350ae4fe5fab","tid":1243392,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:25:55.000Z","msg":"趁而家狗打狗，之後我地加多幾腳，話盧生唔like林太，之後話林太因為盧生射個波俾佢，私底下屌一哥。<br />\n<br />\n麥美娟屌林鄭已經睇到佢地出現矛盾。<br />\n<br />\n我地可以話其他官員俾林鄭搞到周身蟻，個個都唔撚想攬上身，但焗住管你班記者同市民問題，同俾人問候...,個個心裏面都屌777。<br />\n<br />\n要俾全世界知，林鄭團隊名存實亡。<br />\n<br />\n到時上街，d官就真係會質問同批評林鄭辦事能力"},{"pid":"3ae154833f5d0a8848a860e18da83d06a2b8fd1d","tid":1243392,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:28:23.000Z","msg":"乜仲有人覺得有分化到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個政府機關慣左咁樣射波 耍太極<br />\n完全唔會有人食"},{"pid":"226d096ac75a12ef9d492d958410b7604ca6e29f","tid":1243392,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:39:40.000Z","msg":"係未發展到私憤個地步姐<br />\n因為而家人地仲做緊果個位，<br />\n但係如果有人頂唔順，俾人問候老母幾百次，咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就好似果位議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75a98ee986808fa6114ce62cb0de87b3cd2f1f34","tid":1243392,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:08:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><